draft.title: SMARTYPANTS DIY Personalised Pet Santa Sack - Create Your Own Dog or Cat Name with Iron On Letters - Large Hessian Christmas Gift Bag with Tartan Paw Design for Furry Friends Holiday Presents
draft.description:
Make your furry friend the star of the show this Christmas with the SMARTYPANTS DIY Personalised Pet Santa Sack! There's no better way to include your beloved cat or dog in the family festivities than with a special sack filled just for them. This kit makes it fun and easy to create a lasting keepsake. You receive a beautifully designed hessian sack featuring a festive tartan paw print and the charming phrase 'Sleigh Bells & Waggy Tails'.

We also include a full A3 sheet of high-quality red DTF (Direct to Film) iron-on letters, allowing you to customise the sack with your pet's name right at home. Crafted from durable, eco-friendly hessian fabric with a secure drawstring, this sack is perfect for filling with toys and treats. It's a wonderful, reusable alternative to wrapping paper that you and your pet can enjoy for many Christmases to come.

bullets: Personalise For Pets – Create a unique Christmas sack for your beloved dog or cat with our easy DIY kit including iron-on letters for a truly special touch this festive season.
Premium Hessian Fabric – Crafted from durable premium hessian fabric this charming sack features a secure drawstring closure to keep your pet's festive treats and toys safely inside.
Reusable Festive Fun – A spacious and eco-friendly alternative to wrapping paper this sack can be reused every year making it a sustainable and cherished part of your holiday traditions.
Vibrant DTF Quality – The charming tartan paw design is printed with vibrant colours and the included A3 DTF sheet ensures your pet's name looks bold and lasts for years to come.
Perfect Gift Idea – An ideal gift for any pet lover this DIY sack kit is perfect for filling with presents or using as a delightful piece of festive home decoration by the tree.
